        &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jacobsherin.com/posts/2025-08-18-bplustree-struct-hack/#adding-new-members-in-a-derived-class&quot;&gt;Adding New Members In A Derived Class&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
