        &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jacobsherin.com/posts/2025-08-18-bplustree-struct-hack/#hidden-data-type-assumptions&quot;&gt;Hidden Data Type Assumptions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
